---
const title = 'Momentum — Time tracking for makers';
const description =
  'Momentum helps makers track real project time in seconds, with a frictionless macOS workflow and Raycast extension.';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0b1020" />
    <title>{title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #070b17;
        --bg-2: #0d1328;
        --card: rgba(20, 27, 52, 0.72);
        --text: #edf2ff;
        --muted: #b6c0e4;
        --accent: #8ea9ff;
        --line: #2a3667;
        --ok: #8ee4b7;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; color-scheme: dark; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 85% -10%, rgba(132, 156, 255, 0.25), transparent 35%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 10% 10%, rgba(91, 129, 255, 0.22), transparent 30%),
          linear-gradient(170deg, var(--bg-2), var(--bg));
        color: var(--text);
        min-height: 100vh;
        -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(124, 156, 255, 0.2);
      }
      .skip-link {
        position: absolute;
        left: -9999px;
        top: 0;
        background: #fff;
        color: #111;
        padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .skip-link:focus-visible { left: 1rem; top: 1rem; z-index: 9999; }

      .container { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 1.2rem 1rem 4.5rem; }

      .nav {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.6rem;
      }
      .brand {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.6rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--text);
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .brand-dot {
        width: 10px;
        height: 10px;
        border-radius: 99px;
        background: var(--accent);
        box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(142, 169, 255, 0.8);
      }
      .nav-links {
        display: inline-flex;
        gap: 0.8rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .nav-links a {
        color: #c6d0f3;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.93rem;
      }
      .nav-links a:hover { color: #fff; }

      .hero {
        position: relative;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(28, 39, 80, 0.55), rgba(15, 22, 48, 0.55));
        border-radius: 22px;
        padding: 2.2rem;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .hero::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: auto -35% -45% auto;
        width: 480px;
        height: 480px;
        border-radius: 100%;
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(142, 169, 255, 0.18), transparent 60%);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.45rem;
        background: rgba(144, 170, 255, 0.14);
        border: 1px solid rgba(160, 182, 255, 0.35);
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: #dbe4ff;
        padding: 0.35rem 0.7rem;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.95rem;
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3.6rem);
        line-height: 1.05;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        max-width: 13ch;
        text-wrap: balance;
      }
      .lead {
        margin: 0.9rem 0 0;
        max-width: 65ch;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1.03rem;
      }
      .hero-actions {
        margin-top: 1.4rem;
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }

      .btn {
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        cursor: pointer;
        transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
        touch-action: manipulation;
      }
      .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
      .btn:focus-visible,
      input:focus-visible,
      summary:focus-visible,
      .nav-links a:focus-visible {
        outline: 2px solid var(--accent);
        outline-offset: 2px;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .btn.primary { background: var(--accent); color: #0b1020; }
      .btn.primary:hover { background: #a5bbff; }
      .btn.ghost { border-color: #425590; color: var(--text); }
      .btn.ghost:hover { background: rgba(26, 36, 72, 0.75); }

      .proof {
        margin-top: 1.2rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 0.7rem;
      }
      .pill {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 999px;
        padding: 0.38rem 0.72rem;
        color: #c8d3fa;
        font-size: 0.86rem;
        background: rgba(13, 19, 40, 0.55);
      }

      .section { margin-top: 2.2rem; scroll-margin-top: 1.5rem; }
      h2 {
        margin: 0 0 0.7rem;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        letter-spacing: -0.01em;
        text-wrap: balance;
      }
      .section-intro {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        max-width: 68ch;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.9rem;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }
      .card {
        background: var(--card);
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 1rem;
        backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      }
      .card h3 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 1.03rem;
      }
      .card p {
        margin: 0.55rem 0 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .steps {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.8rem;
      }
      .step {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 0.9rem;
        background: rgba(12, 18, 48, 0.68);
      }
      .step strong { color: #fff; }
      .step p { margin: 0.45rem 0 0; color: var(--muted); }

      .screenshots {
        margin-top: 1rem;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.85rem;
      }
      .shot {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 16px;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: rgba(15, 21, 48, 0.86);
      }
      .shot .ph {
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #26346b, #101838);
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        color: #b9c7ff;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .shot p { margin: 0; padding: 0.85rem; color: #c7d2fa; }

      .waitlist {
        margin-top: 2.2rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(24, 34, 72, 0.8), rgba(14, 20, 42, 0.8));
        padding: 1.25rem;
      }
      .waitlist p { margin: 0 0 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); }
      .waitlist form {
        display: flex;
        gap: 0.6rem;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
      }
      .input-wrap { flex: 1; min-width: 240px; }
      label { display: block; margin: 0 0 0.35rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #d0dafd; }
      input[type="email"] {
        width: 100%;
        border: 1px solid #465a98;
        background: #0c1230;
        color: var(--text);
        padding: 0.75rem 0.9rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
      }
      input[type="email"]::placeholder { color: #90a3dd; }

      .faq {
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }
      details {
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
        background: rgba(15, 21, 48, 0.72);
      }
      details + details { margin-top: 0.65rem; }
      summary { cursor: pointer; font-weight: 600; }
      details p { margin: 0.55rem 0 0; }

      .cta {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 1.1rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: rgba(13, 19, 40, 0.75);
      }
      .cta h2 { margin-bottom: 0.45rem; }
      .cta p { margin: 0 0 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); }

      footer {
        margin-top: 2.7rem;
        text-align: center;
        color: #94a4da;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 740px) {
        .hero { padding: 1.4rem; }
        .nav { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
      }

      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        *, *::before, *::after {
          animation: none !important;
          transition: none !important;
          scroll-behavior: auto !important;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to Content</a>

    <main class="container" id="main-content">
      <header class="nav">
        <a class="brand" href="#top">
          <span class="brand-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          Momentum
        </a>
        <nav class="nav-links" aria-label="Primary">
          <a href="#features">Features</a>
          <a href="#how-it-works">How It Works</a>
          <a href="#screenshots">Screenshots</a>
          <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        </nav>
      </header>

      <section class="hero section" id="top">
        <div class="badge">Built for Focused Makers</div>
        <h1>Track Real Project Time, Then Ship with Clarity.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Momentum gives you practical visibility on where your hours actually go. Log work in seconds,
          organize by project, and turn weekly tracking into better decisions. No spreadsheet overhead. No friction tax.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a class="btn primary" href="#waitlist">Join Waitlist</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="#how-it-works">See How It Works</a>
        </div>
        <div class="proof" aria-label="Highlights">
          <span class="pill">Native macOS workflow</span>
          <span class="pill">Raycast extension included</span>
          <span class="pill">Project-first analytics</span>
          <span class="pill">Built and used daily</span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="features">
        <h2>Why Momentum Feels Different</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Most trackers optimize for admin teams. Momentum optimizes for builders who care about output.</p>
        <div class="grid">
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Capture in Seconds</h3>
            <p>Start and stop sessions instantly, so tracking supports deep work instead of interrupting it.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Organize by Project</h3>
            <p>See effort by project and make smarter trade-offs based on real time spent, not guesses.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="card">
            <h3>Raycast-Powered Logging</h3>
            <p>Capture from anywhere on your Mac with one command and zero context switching.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="how-it-works">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">A lightweight loop you can sustain every day.</p>
        <div class="steps">
          <article class="step">
            <strong>1. Start a Session</strong>
            <p>Pick a project and begin tracking in seconds.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <strong>2. Log with Context</strong>
            <p>Attach sessions to real project work, not vague buckets.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="step">
            <strong>3. Review and Decide</strong>
            <p>Use weekly signals to adjust priorities and ship with confidence.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section" id="screenshots">
        <h2>Screenshots</h2>
        <p class="section-intro">Replace these placeholders with your real captures for launch.</p>
        <div class="screenshots">
          <article class="shot">
            <div class="ph">Dashboard screenshot</div>
            <p>Get an instant view of project totals, trends, and where momentum is building.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="shot">
            <div class="ph">Session logging screenshot</div>
            <p>Track focused work with minimal friction and keep your sprint rhythm intact.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="shot">
            <div class="ph">Raycast extension screenshot</div>
            <p>Capture from anywhere on macOS with one shortcut and one command.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="waitlist section" id="waitlist">
        <h2>Get Early Access</h2>
        <p>Momentum is in final polish. Join to get launch updates, early access, and release notes.</p>
        <form action="https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id" method="POST">
          <div class="input-wrap">
            <label for="waitlist-email">Email</label>
            <input
              id="waitlist-email"
              type="email"
              name="email"
              placeholder="name@company.com…"
              autocomplete="email"
              spellcheck="false"
              required
            />
          </div>
          <button class="btn primary" type="submit">Join Waitlist</button>
        </form>
      </section>

      <section class="faq section" id="faq">
        <h2>FAQ</h2>
        <details>
          <summary>Who is Momentum for?</summary>
          <p>Developers, designers, and makers doing project-based work who want clear time data without admin drag.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>Do I need to track every minute?</summary>
          <p>No. Track enough to make better decisions and keep your weekly planning grounded in reality.</p>
        </details>
        <details>
          <summary>What’s Different vs Generic Time Trackers?</summary>
          <p>Momentum is optimized for maker workflows: speed, project context, and a native macOS + Raycast flow.</p>
        </details>
      </section>

      <section class="cta section">
        <h2>Track Less Admin. Ship More Product.</h2>
        <p>Turn work logs into sharper priorities and consistent progress every week.</p>
        <a class="btn primary" href="#waitlist">Join Waitlist</a>
      </section>

      <footer>Built by Miguel · Momentum</footer>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
